"{\"uid\": \"techradar.com-pro-security-microsoft-reveals-major-russian-cyber-threats-that-looked-to-target-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Major Russian misinformation campaign has Paris Olympics in its sights  When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.Here's how it works.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9209837097228369, \"rank\": 0.08577831764734531, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 42, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Multiple Russian state-sponsored threat actors are actively running misinformation campaigns regarding theSummer Olympic Gamesthat are due in Paris, France, this summer.\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 184, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9209837097228369, \"rank\": 0.08577831764734531, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996150002803, \"rank\": 3.849997753713412e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 324, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9838848280033999, \"rank\": 0.01125881780391707, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The goal of the campaigns, apparently, is to make people afraid and have them avoid the event altogether.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheMicrosoftThreat Analysis Center (MTAC) recently published anew reportoutlining at least two separate threat actor groups, Storm-1679, and Storm-1099, working at the same time, and for the same goal.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Readers might remember the latter from previous reports, when Storm-1099 was attributed with a misinformation campaign that Ukraine was selling donated weapons to Hamas to commit atrocities in Israel.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999998391326829, \"rank\": 1.0024007141692673e-07, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.899256641336836e-12, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}, {\"begin\": 848, \"end\": 854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999263859563, \"rank\": 6.922636605919807e-08, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For these campaigns, the groups are doing a number of things, including spoofing popular news outlets in France and elsewhere in Europe, as well asimpersonatingactors and celebrities.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9838848280033999, \"rank\": 0.01125881780391707, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, Microsoft says the misinformation masters created a fake Netflix documentary called \\\"Olympics Has Fallen\\\", sporting the streaming service's logo and narrated by an AI-generated Tom Cruise voice.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.9999891178118593, \"rank\": 1.0882299662656753e-05, \"text\": \"Microsoft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}, {\"begin\": 1108, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.9999999999606644, \"rank\": 3.933523803250371e-11, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Further analysis confirmed the fake documentary used AI-generated audio resembling Cruise's voice to imply his participation, spoofed Netflix's iconic intro scene and corporate branding, and promoted bogus five-star reviews from reputable media outlets like the New York Times, the Washington Post, and the BBC, all amid slick computer-generated special effects,\\\" the report noted.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.9999999999606644, \"rank\": 3.933523803250371e-11, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}, {\"begin\": 1510, \"end\": 1518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999850228961, \"rank\": 1.4941147804733265e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington\", \"score\": 0.7306502786521945, \"rank\": 0.3678268643426096, \"text\": \"Washington\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington\"}, {\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9996933070862322, \"rank\": 0.0003067635069682004, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russian state-sponsored hackers have a history of meddling in both national and global events, with the goal of disrupting and spreading misinformation.\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9209837097228369, \"rank\": 0.08577831764734531, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US presidential elections, 2018 Winter Olympic Games in South Korea, French P